{
  "stem": "9943.5",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I told them I'm going to go to Moscow.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I got the permission.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I got the permit, and I left two years later, Tashkent.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I came to Moscow.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I came to Moscow.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Then there was a problem-- that they wanted us to go to-- to Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "In Moscow, you don't have a right to leave unless you have work.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "To have work, you have to have place to live.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So there was-- was all that things how it went, and how I managed to be in Moscow.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I was-- stayed in Moscow and worked in the hospital for-- [RUSSIAN].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It means expertness in being able to work.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "People from all Moscow were sent to that hospital to decide whether they have-- can change their work or not.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "That was an interesting-- as a neurologist, I worked.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And it was an interesting job, because you had to make a diagnosis about what's the matter with a person, and these were difficult cases.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Well, so I worked in this hospital.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "In the meantime, I met Polish people from Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I met some-- one of them that I was the doctor in Warsaw, his son.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "These were those rich communists from Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Some of them got to-- to Moscow.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And it was called Zwiazek Patriotio Polskich.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "They're the Zwiazek.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "That's the Association of Polish Patriots.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So through these Polish Patriots, I-- I got the possibility to leave Moscow to Poland because I knew foreign languages.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They needed someone that would be able to interpret [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] to interpret-- to-- the foreign correspondence what was going on because people started-- to do-- foreign correspondence started to come to Russia and then to-- to [? new ?] Poland.",
      "word_count": 43
    }
  ],
